## Project Overview
{{.Description}}

## Tech Stack
- **Language**: C# 13
- **Framework**: ASP.NET Core (.NET 9.0)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 17 (via Docker)
- **ORM**: Entity Framework Core 9.0
- **API Docs**: Swagger / OpenAPI

## Project Structure
- `Controllers/` - API controllers
- `Models/` - Entity classes and DTOs
- `Data/` - EF Core DbContext
- `Services/` - Business logic layer
- `docs/supporting/` - Supporting documentation

## Development Commands
```bash
make start    # Start Docker Compose stack
make stop     # Stop all services
make test     # Run tests
make build    # Build project
make run      # Run locally
make watch    # Run with hot reload
```

## Conventions
- Use dependency injection for all services
- Controllers should be thin (delegate to services)
- Entity models in `Models/` namespace
- Use async/await for I/O operations
- Configuration via appsettings.json with environment overrides
- Use `ILogger<T>` for structured logging
